    • allTypes

      public static javafx.collections.ObservableList<String> allTypes()
      LAMBDA - Get All Appointment Types. Returns an Observable List of Appointment Types from the db. The lambda expression is completed within the forEach loop of the allAppointments list and takes each appointment and gets the type and adds it to the allTypes list.
      Returns:
      list of appointment types as Strings.
